window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nathan Myers and the crew of the <i>Legacy </i>find themselves at war with the predatory races and murderous corruption prevalent throughout the galaxy. The shadowy criminal figures who stand to lose the most from Nathan's victories has put a billion-credit bounty on his head. To make matters worse, the Scrun and Murlaks have assassination squads actively pursuing Nathan and his crew. In order to survive, Nathan must find allies willing to stand with him. Finding an ally without ulterior motives is easier said than done. No matter the odds, Nathan and his crew will battle through hell and back, for the good of all!</p>"; 
